{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@_NSRange","text":"NSRange","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"range","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCoordinates:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"coords","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"range","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The range of vertices to replace. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"location"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the first vertex you are replacing, with ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being the first vertex, ","type":"text"},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"being the second vertex, and so on. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"length","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" field indicates the number","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of vertices to replace.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of coordinates defining part of the shape. The data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this array is copied to the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"coords"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion